    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink24-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> parattaiyaruḷḷum oruttiyaiviṭṭu oruttiyaip paṟṟi oḻukukiṉṟāṉ eṉpatu kēṭṭa
          tōḻi vāyilāy vantār kēṭpat talaimakaṭkuc colliyatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink24">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> tāycāp piṟakkum puḷḷik kaḷvaṉoṭu</l>
          <l> piḷḷai tiṉṉu mutalait tavaṉū</l>
          <l> reytiṉa ṉākiṉṟu kollō makiḻnaṉ</l>
          <l> polantoṭi teḷirppa muyaṅkiyavar</l>
          <l> nalaṅkoṇṭu tuṟappa tevaṉko laṉṉāy.</l>

        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> His village is one of crocodiles that eat [their own] young</l>
          <l rend='indent2'> and spotted crabs that are born when [their] mother dies.</l>
          <l> Is it that he reached [there], the delightful man?</l>
          <l> His taking the beauty of those he embraces– so that [their] golden</l>
          <l> bracelets sparkle – [and] abandoning [of them]: </l>
          <l> What [of it], mother? </l>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
